"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.21.6\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.21.6</span> 标题：刑架和其他刑具（rack and other instruments of torture）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἄξων</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：axōn)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc9:20\">4MA 9:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：καταπέλτης</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：katapeltēs)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc11:26\">4MA 11:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc8:13\">4MA 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc9:26\">4MA 9:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc11:9\">4MA 11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc18:20\">4MA 18:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：στρέβλη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：streblē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir33:27\">SIR 33:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc7:4\">4MA 7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc7:14\">4MA 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc8:11\">4MA 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc8:24\">4MA 8:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc9:22\">4MA 9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc14:12\">4MA 14:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc15:24\">4MA 15:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc15:25\">4MA 15:25</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：στρεβλωτήριον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：streblōtērion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc8:13\">4MA 8:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：τροχός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：trochos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc5:32\">4MA 5:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc8:13\">4MA 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc9:12\">4MA 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc9:17\">4MA 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc9:19\">4MA 9:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc9:20\">4MA 9:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc10:8\">4MA 10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc11:10\">4MA 11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc11:17\">4MA 11:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc15:22\">4MA 15:22</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：τύμπανον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tumpanon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc6:19\">2MA 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc6:28\">2MA 6:28</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>刑架是一个拷问的刑具。受刑者的双手伸过头顶，四肢伸展躺在桌子上。手和脚分别绑在桌子两端的轮子或其他装置上，这些装置把四肢拉得越来越开，给人造成巨大的痛苦。受刑者被这样扯拽的同时，可能还会遭受鞭打或其他方式的身体虐待。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>大多数文化都不知道这种刑具。翻译者最好依循<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 的译法，不要追求准确地描述刑架；例如，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc6:19\">2MA 6:19</a> 中，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 英文意为“严刑拷打的地方”。</p>\n<p>希腊文<em>trochos</em> 的字面意思是“轮子”。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc5:32\">4MA 5:32</a> 中，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 英文意为“拷问人的轮子”。在《次经‧马加比四书》的大多数情况下，“轮子”和刑架相似，都是用来扯拽受刑者的，并且轮子似乎与火一起使用，受刑者在被扯拽的同时，还被火烤灼着。</p>\n<p>同样，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc8:13\">4MA 8:13</a> 中的希腊文<em>katapeltēs</em> 似乎是指一种拉扯四肢、使关节脱臼的刑具。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 把它译为“catapults”（“弹弓”），但<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 译为“pounding machines”（“投石车”）。但这似乎不符合<a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc11:9\">4MA 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc11:10\">4MA 11:10</a> 中描述的酷刑，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 英文意为“他将要受刑的地方”。</p>\n<p>《次经‧马加比四书》所列的部分刑具可能是更大刑具的构件；例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc11:10\">4MA 11:10</a> 中的“楔子”（“wedge”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ，希腊文<em>sfēn</em> ）、“铁夹子”（<em>podagra sidērous</em> ）和“轮子”（<em>trochiaios</em> ）在施行<em>katapeltēs</em> 酷刑时都会用到。</p>\n<p>希腊文<em>axōn</em> 通常指的是轮子的轴（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">8.3 轮、车轮 (wheel)&lt;REALIA:8.3&gt;</a> ）。然而，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc9:20\">4MA 9:20</a> 中，它不是指车轮的一个部件，而是指静止不动的刑讯机器的一个部分。轮子是其运转机构的一部分，这些轮子就像马车上的轮子一样，围着一个中心轴转动。</p>\n<p>《次经‧马加比四书》还提到了其他一些刑具。这些刑具的结构大多不明确。我们在这里列出它们的名称以及翻译建议。主要有：</p>\n<p>\n            <em>arthrembolon</em>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc8:13\">4MA 8:13</a> “关节脱臼器”（“joint-dislocator”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）、“牵拉架”（“stretching frame”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）</p>\n<p>\n            <em>daktulēthra</em>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc8:13\">4MA 8:13</a> “拇指夹”（“thumbscrew”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）、“铁钳”（“iron clamps”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）</p>\n<p>\n            <em>daktulēthra</em>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc8:13\">4MA 8:13</a> “骨头轧碎器”（“bone-crusher”，可能与轮子有关）</p>\n<p>\n            <em>cheir sidēra</em>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc8:13\">4MA 8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc11:10\">4MA 11:10</a> “带尖钩的铁手套”（“iron gauntlets having sharp hooks”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）、“末端有尖钩的重铁棒”（“heavy iron club with sharp hooks on its end”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
